---
interface Props {
  section: string;
  fallbackBody: string;
}
const { section, fallbackBody } = Astro.props;
---

{/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{/* CHALLENGES                                                                 */}
{/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "challenges" && (
  <div class="space-y-6">

    <!-- Overview -->
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      Apex Trader Funding offers two account types — <strong>Tradovate</strong> and <strong>Rithmic</strong> — with account sizes from <strong>$25,000 to $300,000</strong>. The core difference is the trading platform each account operates on. Each type provides various funded account sizes with different contract limits, trailing thresholds, and drawdown structures.
    </p>

    <!-- Account type cards -->
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Tradovate Accounts</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Browser-based platform with mobile and desktop access. TradingView integration. Ideal for traders who want flexibility and multi-device trading.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Rithmic Accounts</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">High-speed execution with low-latency data feeds. Compatible with NinjaTrader. Ideal for advanced traders and algorithmic strategies.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Evaluation process -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
      <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">How Does the Evaluation Work?</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-slate-400 font-bold">•</span>One-step evaluation with a minimum of <strong>7 trading days</strong></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-slate-400 font-bold">•</span>Profit targets are <strong>fixed dollar amounts</strong>, not percentages — starting at $1,500 for 25K accounts</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-slate-400 font-bold">•</span>Static accounts have lower targets — 100K Static requires only $2,000 vs $6,000 for 100K Full</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-slate-400 font-bold">•</span>Upon passing, you get <strong>100% profit split on first $25K</strong>, then 75%–95% thereafter</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-slate-400 font-bold">•</span>No scaling requirements on funded accounts</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Tradovate accounts table -->
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Tradovate Accounts</h4>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Account</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Contracts (Micros)</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Profit Goal</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Trailing Threshold</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Monthly Cost</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">25K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">4 (40)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$1,500</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$1,500</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$167</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">50K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">10 (100)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$3,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$2,500</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$187</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">100K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">14 (140)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$6,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$3,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$297</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">100K Static</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">2 (20)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$2,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">None</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$157</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">150K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">17 (170)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$9,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$5,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$397</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">250K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">27 (270)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$15,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$6,500</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$497</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">300K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">35 (350)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$20,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$7,500</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$597</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Rithmic accounts table -->
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Rithmic Accounts</h4>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Account</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Contracts (Micros)</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Profit Goal</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Trailing Threshold</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Platform & Data Fees</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Monthly Cost</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">25K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">4 (40)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$1,500</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$1,500</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">NinjaTrader ($75) & Data ($55)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$157</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">50K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">10 (100)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$3,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$2,500</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">NinjaTrader ($75) & Data ($55)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$177</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">100K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">14 (140)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$6,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$3,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">NinjaTrader ($75) & Data ($55)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$297</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">100K Static</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">2 (20)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$2,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">None</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">NinjaTrader ($75) & Data ($55)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$147</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">150K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">17 (170)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$9,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$5,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">NinjaTrader ($75) & Data ($55)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$397</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">250K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">27 (270)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$15,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$6,500</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">NinjaTrader ($75) & Data ($55)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$497</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">300K Full</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">35 (350)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$20,000</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$7,500</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">NinjaTrader ($75) & Data ($55)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-red-600">$597</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Verdict -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-red-300 bg-red-50 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-red-900 leading-relaxed">
        <strong>Verdict on Challenges — 4/10:</strong> With account sizes from $25,000 to $300,000 and contracts from 4 up to 35, Apex's offerings cater to different trading volumes. However, the <strong>high monthly subscription fees</strong> ($147–$597/mo) make this one of the most expensive evaluation programs in the industry. Unlike most prop firms that charge a one-time fee, Apex's recurring costs can add up quickly if you don't pass.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
)}

{/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{/* SPREADS (Pricing & Commission Fees)                                        */}
{/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "spreads" && (
  <div class="space-y-6">

    <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      Apex Trader Funding's costs can accumulate over time, with monthly fees for evaluation accounts, activation fees for funded accounts, and commission charges per trade. These ongoing expenses, especially with add-ons like Level 2 data, can significantly impact monthly costs for active traders.
    </p>

    <!-- Activation fees -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
      <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Activation Fees (Funded Accounts)</h4>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Account Type</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Monthly Fee</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Lifetime Fee</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">Rithmic</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">$85/mo</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-600">$130 – $340</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">Tradovate</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">$105/mo</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-600">$150 – $360</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Commission fees -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
      <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Commission Fees</h4>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Instrument</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Tradovate (Round Turn)</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Rithmic (Round Turn)</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">E-mini S&P 500 (ES)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$3.10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-600">$3.98</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">Micro E-mini S&P 500 (MES)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-600">$1.04</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-600">$1.02</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Data fees -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-4">
      <p class="text-sm text-amber-900 leading-relaxed">
        <strong>Additional Data Fees:</strong> Level 1 market data is included. Level 2 data (depth of market) costs <strong>$41+/month</strong> plus a $2 processing fee. These subscriptions are managed through the respective platforms and do not renew automatically.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Verdict -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-red-300 bg-red-50 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-red-900 leading-relaxed">
        <strong>Verdict on Pricing — 4/10:</strong> With monthly evaluation fees, activation charges for funded accounts ($85–$360), and additional data costs, Apex Trader Funding's expenses add up quickly. The commission fees themselves are reasonable, but the <strong>recurring subscription model</strong> makes it significantly more expensive than prop firms offering one-time evaluation fees.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
)}

{/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{/* MARKETS (Futures Markets)                                                  */}
{/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "markets" && (
  <div class="space-y-6">

    <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      Apex Trader Funding offers <strong>46 futures markets</strong> in total, covering currency, equity, agriculture, energy, metal, and cryptocurrency futures. Supported exchanges include the <strong>CME, CBOT, COMEX, and NYMEX</strong>.
    </p>

    <!-- Market categories -->
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 text-sm">Currency Futures</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Euro FX (6E), British Pound (6B), Japanese Yen (6J) and more</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 text-sm">Equity Futures</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">E-mini S&P 500 (ES), Mini-DOW (YM), E-mini NASDAQ 100 (NQ)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 text-sm">Agricultural Futures</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Corn (ZC), Wheat (ZW), Lean Hogs (HE) and more</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 text-sm">Energy Futures</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Crude Oil (CL), Natural Gas (NG), Heating Oil (HO)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 text-sm">Metal Futures</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Gold (GC), Silver (SI), Copper (HG), E-Micro Gold (MGC)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 text-sm">Crypto Futures</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Micro Bitcoin (MBT), Micro Ether (MET) — micro contracts only</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Verdict -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-red-300 bg-red-50 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-red-900 leading-relaxed">
        <strong>Verdict on Markets — 4/10:</strong> While Apex covers popular high-liquidity futures assets across 46 markets, the selection is <strong>futures-only</strong> with no forex, stocks, or indices outside of futures contracts. Crypto is limited to micro contracts only. The range may feel limited compared to forex prop firms offering hundreds of instruments.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
)}

{/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{/* PLATFORMS (Trading Platforms)                                               */}
{/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "platforms" && (
  <div class="space-y-6">

    <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      Apex Trader Funding supports a wide range of trading platforms across its two main account types. Each platform provides specific tools tailored to different needs, from flexible web-based options to advanced low-latency setups.
    </p>

    <!-- Platform cards -->
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">NinjaTrader 8</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mb-2">Advanced charting, strategy automation, custom indicators. Free license provided.</p>
        <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5">Tradovate & Rithmic</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Tradovate</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mb-2">Browser, mobile, and desktop access. TradingView integration. Intuitive interface.</p>
        <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5">Tradovate Only</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">TradingView</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mb-2">Integrated charting, social trading tools, customisable indicators. Trade directly from charts.</p>
        <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5">Tradovate Only</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">RTrader Pro</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mb-2">High-performance, low-latency data, real-time account monitoring. PC only.</p>
        <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5">Rithmic Only</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Other Rithmic platforms -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
      <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Additional Rithmic Platforms</h4>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {["ATAS", "BOOKMAP", "Edge Clear EdgeProX", "Finamark", "Jigsaw Trading", "MotiveWave", "Quantower", "Sierra Chart", "VolFix", "WealthCharts"].map(p => (
          <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1">{p}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Trading rules table -->
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Trading Rules</h4>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Rule</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Status</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-slate-700">Trailing Threshold</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right"><span class="text-amber-600 font-semibold">Follows profits (full accounts)</span></td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-slate-700">Minimum Trading Days</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right"><span class="text-slate-900 font-semibold">7 days</span></td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-slate-700">Consistency Rules</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right"><span class="text-amber-600 font-semibold">Required on funded</span></td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-slate-700">Fully Automated Systems</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right"><span class="text-red-600 font-semibold">Banned</span></td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-slate-700">Semi-Automated Systems</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right"><span class="text-green-600 font-semibold">Allowed (if monitored)</span></td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-slate-700">Copy Trading</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right"><span class="text-red-600 font-semibold">Banned</span></td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-slate-700">News Trading</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-right"><span class="text-amber-600 font-semibold">Allowed (directional bias required)</span></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Verdict -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-red-300 bg-red-50 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-red-900 leading-relaxed">
        <strong>Verdict on Platforms — 5/10:</strong> Apex offers a good range of platform options, from multi-device Tradovate to advanced NinjaTrader and RTrader Pro. However, the <strong>ban on fully automated systems and copy trading</strong> on funded accounts limits flexibility. Primary technical support is focused on NinjaTrader, with only partial support for other platforms.
      </p>
